Philippines to Act Only to Contain Volatilities, Tetangco Says

-- B y   C l a r i s s a   B a t i n o
-- 
2011-09-20T06:42:17Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-20/philippines-to-act-only-to-contain-volatilities-tetangco-says.html
The Philippine central bank will
act “only to contain excessive volatilies in the peso
movement,” Governor Amando Tetangco said today.  The local currency is trading “in line with the region’s,
which are in turn affected by global developments,” Tetangco
said in a mobile-phone text message today in  Manila .  ---With assistance from Cecilia Yap and Karl Lester M. Yap in
Manila.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Clarissa Batino in Manila at 
